  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, post-market, multi-center, non-blinded, single arm study of the&#xD;
      HeartMate 3 Left Ventricular Assist System (LVAS). The objective of this study is to evaluate&#xD;
      the implantation of the HM3 utilizing techniques other than full median sternotomy (e.g.&#xD;
      thoracotomy) and impact on post-implant length of stay.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
